  "description": "Defines a contract for parsing JSON strings into a dictionary of properties.",
  "title": "Interface IJsonParser",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Parsing_IJsonParser'>Interface IJsonParser    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Parsing/IJsonParser.cs#L37'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Defines a contract for parsing JSON strings into a dictionary of properties.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public interface IJsonParser</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.ParseToDictionary(System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.ParseToDictionary(System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Parsing_IJsonParser_ParseToDictionary_System_String_'>ParseToDictionary(string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/Parsing/IJsonParser.cs#L45'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Parses a JSON string into a dictionary of property names and their string values.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>Dictionary&lt;string, string&gt; ParseToDictionary(string json)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>json</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The JSON string to parse.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.dictionary-2'>Dictionary</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>, <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A dictionary containing property names as keys and their string representations as values.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Parsing.IJsonParser.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when json is null.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
